author: The Critical Drinker
description: Was it worth waiting 20 years for Gladiator 2? Was Wicked good enough to rise above the controversy? And how will we all cope now that She-Hulk has been erased from Marvel's marketing? Join me, MauLer, Little Platoon, Chris Gore and History Bro as we find out.
title: Open Bar #119 - Gladiator 2, Wicked, Dune Prophecy, She-Hulk Erased

author: The Critical Drinker
description: Wow, I never could have predicted this, but a short film named 765874 Unification, gave us the final goodbye that Kirk and Spock never got, delivered more heart and soul than 20 years of Modern Trek, and might just have brought a tear to my cynical eye.
title: Star Trek Unification - I'm Not Crying, You're Crying!
